rows.label: qst102105_msg0001
rows.name: Last, huh?

rows.label: qst102105_msg0002
rows.name:
You're late!
How long did you expect us to wait?!

rows.label: qst102105_msg0003
rows.name: Whoa, take it easy...

rows.label: qst102105_msg0004
rows.name:
Defeating five targets took
longer than expected.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0005
rows.name:
That two too many!
Why ignore orders?

rows.label: qst102105_msg0006
rows.name:
They came at me.
Didn't have a choice.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0007
rows.name:
If I'd left them, there might have
been repercussions down the line.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0008
rows.name: ...Phew, that's a relief.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0009
rows.name: What? Why?

rows.label: qst102105_msg0010
rows.name:
'Cos actually, my weapon was acting
kinda weird, so I only killed one.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0011
rows.name:
Really?
Why you not say anything?

rows.label: qst102105_msg0012
rows.name:
So you just hung around here, waiting?
What were you doing?

rows.label: qst102105_msg0013
rows.name: Oh, shut it...

rows.label: qst102105_msg0014
rows.name:
And anyway, what's up with the
precise numbering? Who decided
it's supposed to be 12?

rows.label: qst102105_msg0015
rows.name:
Everyone, just calm down...
Let's not sweat the details.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0016
rows.name:
Arthem's extra kills mean
the mission is now complete.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0017
rows.name:
Nobody tell Bamibami anything!
Not cool!

rows.label: qst102105_msg0018
rows.name: We're done here, so let's report back.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0019
rows.name: Meet you there?

rows.label: qst102105_msg0020
rows.name: ...Fine by me.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0021
rows.name: Fine by Bamibami!

rows.label: qst102105_msg0022
rows.name:
Huh?!
Oh, uh, OK then...

rows.label: qst102105_msg0023
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]This doesn't help me at all...
